data.current_description: Sets the access control policy on the specified `Note` or `Occurrence`. Attempting to call this method without these permissions will result in a ` `PERMISSION_DENIED` error. data.summary_suggestion: Set IAM policy on occurrence or note resource
data.description_suggestion: Sets the Identity and Access Management (IAM) policy on the specified `Note` or `Occurrence` resource. This operation controls who has access to the resource and what permissions they have. Requires `containeranalysis.notes.setIamPolicy` permission for Notes or `containeranalysis.occurrences.setIamPolicy` permission for Occurrences. Returns the updated `Policy` object. Resource format: `projects/{PROJECT_ID}/occurrences/{OCCURRENCE_ID}` for Occurrences or `projects/{PROJECT_ID}/notes/{NOTE_ID}` for Notes. Returns `PERMISSION_DENIED` if caller lacks required permissions, and `NOT_FOUND` if the resource does not exist.

Requires `containeranalysis.notes.list` or `containeranalysis.occurrences.list` permission on the project. Returns a `TestIamPermissionsResponse` containing the subset of requested permissions that the caller actually has. Resource format: `projects/{PROJECT_ID}/occurrences/{OCCURRENCE_ID}` for Occurrences or `projects/{PROJECT_ID}/notes/{NOTE_ID}` for Notes.
